  assert(total == 15, "sum 1..5: {total}");
```

Squares via for loop with index tracking.

```rust
  idx = 0;
  for s in squares(4) {
    idx += 1;
    if idx == 1 { assert(s == 1, "sq1: {s}"); }
    if idx == 2 { assert(s == 4, "sq2: {s}"); }
    if idx == 3 { assert(s == 9, "sq3: {s}"); }
    if idx == 4 { assert(s == 16, "sq4: {s}"); }
